H0.text: Whose second 'breadfruit voyage' as captain was on the ship HMS Providence, 1791-94. Captain James Cook

H1.text: Whose second 'breadfruit voyage' as captain was on the ship HMS Providence, 1791-94. Captain George Vancouver

H2.text: Whose second 'breadfruit voyage' as captain was on the ship HMS Providence, 1791-94. Captain Matthew Flinders

H3.text: Whose second 'breadfruit voyage' as captain was on the ship HMS Providence, 1791-94. Admiral Bligh

A4.text: It was Bligh's second 'Breadfruit Voyage', following his ill-fated voyage on HMS Bounty.

A5.text: Flinders joined Captain William Bligh's expedition on HMS Providence transporting breadfruit from Tahiti to Jamaica.
